{"tid":1777424,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★【工展會】支客 郭小姐：不擔心危險 因兒子在香港讀書！何先生：不擔心，回有警察","createTime":"2019-12-10T08:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T10:14:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8cae5e22de29ad58daab2156a55c051c310b9578","tid":1777424,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:19:22.000Z","msg":"一年一度的工展會今日（10日）如期開幕，以往工展會都會吸引不少內地客前來掃貨，但在今年的反修例示威不穩情況下，不少展商預計內地客會較往年少。有從深圳搭東鐵過來的內地客郭小姐表示，自己的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兒子在香港讀書</span></strong>，知道香港發生什麼事，不會擔心這裡有危險；而經港珠澳大橋前來工展會的珠海客人何先生亦不覺得香港情況混亂，「不擔心，不會亂，亂了<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">還有警察</span></strong>！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/408249/%E5%B7%A5%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%83-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%A2%E9%A6%96%E6%97%A5%E5%85%A5%E5%A0%B4%E6%8E%83%E8%B2%A8-%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F408249%2F%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25B1%2595%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%258E%2583%25E8%25B2%25A8-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2587%25BC%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E7%259F%25A5%25E9%2581%2593%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=d95c7b1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/408249/%E5%B7%A5%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%83-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%A2%E9%A6%96%E6%97%A5%E5%85%A5%E5%A0%B4%E6%8E%83%E8%B2%A8-%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC</a>"},{"pid":"0cca0ab3f96ccf9b75ff76074e0222a0998d896c","tid":1777